  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long time ago, AIRAN was created and sent to Earth to aid in its development. Thousands of years later, the planet is degraded and being destroyed by those she helped create. Now she must fight her greatest enemy: the human civilization. Take your seat and help her neutralize this threat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AIRANBLADE</strong> is a 3D vertical progression action game, like the best classic shoot 'em up games, which were very popular in the 80s and 90s. Fight against squadrons of enemy aircrafts and gigantic bosses. All of this to the sound of exciting electronic music, beautiful special effects, and lots of explosions and lasers coming from all corners.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751890/extras/c8ac0fc83950b70b23196fc1f63c411a.poster.avif?t=1733431120\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751890/extras/c8ac0fc83950b70b23196fc1f63c411a.webm?t=1733431120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751890/extras/c8ac0fc83950b70b23196fc1f63c411a.mp4?t=1733431120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A long time ago, AIRAN was created and sent to Earth to aid in its development. Thousands of years later, the planet is degraded and being destroyed by those she helped create. Now she must fight her greatest enemy: the human civilization. Take your seat and help her neutralize this threat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>AIRANBLADE</strong> is a 3D vertical progression action game, like the best classic shoot 'em up games, which were very popular in the 80s and 90s. Fight against squadrons of enemy aircrafts and gigantic bosses. All of this to the sound of exciting electronic music, beautiful special effects, and lots of explosions and lasers coming from all corners.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751890/extras/c8ac0fc83950b70b23196fc1f63c411a.poster.avif?t=1733431120\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751890/extras/c8ac0fc83950b70b23196fc1f63c411a.webm?t=1733431120\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2751890/extras/c8ac0fc83950b70b23196fc1f63c411a.mp4?t=1733431120\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
